        <item>
            <title>2.3.0</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 17:22:23 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>47</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.3.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Features
- Cmd+click a file link in chat to open it in the macOS default app (e.g., Xcode for .swift files) instead of the built-in viewer

### Changes
- Teleporting a cloud session now shows a full progress overlay with stage labels (Connecting, Downloading, Switching to branch) instead of a blank screen
- Session titles now use conversation context from multiple prompts for more representative titles
- Session titles are more stable — short follow-up messages like "thanks" no longer overwrite them
- Sidebar now refreshes session titles on every prompt so rows stay current
]]></description>
